<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3243048>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. A. Canthidium gigas Balthasar, 1939, hypomerum with complete hypomeral carina. B. Canthidium kelleri (Martínez et al., 1964), hypomerum with incomplete hypomeral carina. C. Disc of pronotum completely punctated. D. Disc of pronotum with indefinite punctation. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3243048/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3243050>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Canthidium gigas Balthasar, 1939. A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Dorsal view of aedeagus. D. Lateral view of aedeagus. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3243050/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3243052>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Canthidium bokermanni (Martínez et al., 1964). A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view of aedeagus. C. Dorsal view of aedeagus. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3243052/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

